title: Smallville - Alien 009 (2014) (Digital) (JK-Empire)
description:
Written by: Bryan Q. Miller
Pencils: Edgar Salazar
Cover by: Cat Staggs

The hit CW show has ended, but the Smallville story continues. Superman has revealed his alien heritage, but will the people of Earth still accept him?

Batman and Jim Gordon are working together to solve the mystery, but Bruce doesn't like what he's finding. And in Russia, things for Clark go from bad to worse.
